parameters.name: EndTime
parameters.description:
The end of the time range to query. Unit: milliseconds.

> If the ID of the trace is 30 characters in length, this parameter is optional. Otherwise, this parameter is required.

parameters.name: StartTime
parameters.description:
The beginning of the time range to query. Unit: milliseconds.

> If the ID of the trace is 30 characters in length, this parameter is optional. Otherwise, this parameter is required.

parameters.name: TraceID
parameters.description: The trace ID. You can log on to the ARMS console and obtain the trace ID on the **Trace Query** page or **Interface Snapshot** tab.
